________________________________________
ğŸ” Security Insight
â€¢	Port Exposure: Listener opens TCP port 5000, which can be targeted
â€¢	Risk: If the terminal is left unattended, it can be hijacked or misused
â€¢	Relevance in Cybersecurity: Common method in red teaming, used to open backdoors or initiate reverse shells
